| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4843 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 22c730cc-462f-52e5-a3a9-93a34e585e72"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
